data.description:
Price Improvement - Seller Will Contribute $10,000 Towards Closing Costs or Rate Buy Down YOUR CHOICE!

Motivated Sellers - Your Dream Home Awaits!

This Acadian water front beauty offers 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with an open living concept and impressive 20-foot ceilings, allowing an abundance of natural light to fill the space.

The heart of this home is a spacious kitchen with an oversized island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, and ample storage space. The primary bedroom is a retreat with a balcony overlooking the lake, a large bath featuring double vanities, an oversized soaking tub, and a separate ceramic tile shower. 

Entertainment is a breeze in this open, bright, and airy floor plan, perfect for hosting gatherings. The property comes complete with a resort-style pool, a scenic walking trail, a dog park, a fishing pier, a basketball court, a clubhouse, and a fitness center. 

Enjoy one of the largest lots in the community with 10,000 square feet and smart home features for added convenience and security.

Live like you are on vacation with spectacular sunsets on your balcony in the primary suite, providing a tranquil escape. Take advantage of this unique opportunity to own a home that combines luxury and comfort. Sellers are willing to negotiate completely furnished for turn key move in. Act now, as motivated sellers are ready to make your homeownership dreams a reality!
